			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Nice article, however the development of Alchemy toolkit is still active (<a href="http://code.google.com/p/alchemy-2" rel="nofollow">http://code.google.com/p/alchemy-2</a>). They are focusing on Lifted Inference methods, in order to avoid full grounding.  Additionally, another toolkit/library for relational undirected graphical modeling is the Probabilistic Soft Logic (<a href="https://github.com/linqs/psl" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/linqs/psl</a>).</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

